1,"uid":104803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:47:01.000Z","msg":"黑警都係當我地on9 想我地內閧<br />\n所以先派條友入嚟衝<br />\n<br />\n想之後我地人心惶惶覺得衝既有可能係黑警，然後衝既人又被屌<br />\n<br />\n雨傘2.0開波"},{"pid":"f23b4e3fe9af4fca40b2d07e7e71ce42c3e05b0c","tid":1259951,"uid":104803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T19:55:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">所以我地自己要知 邊D時機衝先係合理<br />\n揀岩既時候衝 <br />\n<br />\n唔岩既時機有人衝，根本無人會支持，無論係咪鬼，都係得佢一條友自己7出宇宙<br />\n<br />\n又，黑警鐘意咪join埋一齊衝囉 lol 又如何<br />\n黑警衝黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"afc835d1648ae7f35963d84a05effbba6a671e26","tid":1259951,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:44:08.000Z","msg":"晨早一pish"},{"pid":"b5b6e80bf1cc9f70139e990bf498ae418f7e1a8b","tid":1259951,"uid":104803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"afc835d1648ae7f35963d84a05effbba6a671e26","tid":1259951,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T01:44:08.000Z","msg":"晨早一pish"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T07:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />沉得好快"},{"pid":"9121e65fe11ff67bc829e7fd9456a9c2ab732bf3","tid":1259951,"uid":104803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T10:02:37.000Z","msg":"放工一推"},{"pid":"4848417f3572a51e4720fd3b66ea674e46378156","tid":1259951,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:24:27.000Z","msg":"連登仔出發前睇一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}